00:29:36,241 --> 00:29:37,265
No.

540
00:29:50,055 --> 00:29:52,615
She'll be in surgery for an
hour while we clean and close.

541
00:29:52,791 --> 00:29:53,884
We can go with her?

542
00:29:56,528 --> 00:29:59,191
Have them re-check the calcium.

543
00:30:02,934 --> 00:30:03,993
I wanna thank you.

544
00:30:06,505 --> 00:30:07,768
It's what we do.

545
00:30:07,939 --> 00:30:11,535
- When it goes right.
- There was a minute there...

546
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:14,111
It was like I was
losing everything.

547
00:30:15,047 --> 00:30:17,744
- You can't imagine...
- I'm glad it all worked out for you.

548
00:30:19,017 --> 00:30:21,748
She's a beautiful child.

549
00:30:58,190 --> 00:31:00,421
We're still waiting
on the coroner.

550
00:31:02,427 --> 00:31:04,293
Something else you need?

551
00:31:05,163 --> 00:31:06,324
I wanna clean him up.

552
00:31:07,466 --> 00:31:09,492
We probably have some gauze.

553
00:31:12,671 --> 00:31:14,299
I want the tube out.

554
00:31:15,374 --> 00:31:19,277
Normal procedure is we have
to wait for the coroner before...

555
00:31:19,444 --> 00:31:21,276
I'm familiar with procedure.

556
00:31:25,350 --> 00:31:26,374
Where's your husband?

557
00:31:27,886 --> 00:31:29,582
He's calling our families.

558
00:31:33,692 --> 00:31:35,354
I know, uh...

559
00:31:35,527 --> 00:31:42,400
nothing I can say will probably mean
much to you right now, ahem, but I...

560
00:31:43,368 --> 00:31:46,532
I've seen enough
grief in my life to...

561
