know how
devastating it can be...

562
00:31:53,545 --> 00:31:57,710
and how hard it can
be to find the resilience.

563
00:32:03,655 --> 00:32:05,521
I just hope...

564
00:32:05,857 --> 00:32:10,351
you and your husband find...

565
00:32:10,529 --> 00:32:13,158
Greene. A minute in the hall?

566
00:32:14,199 --> 00:32:16,031
Excuse me.

567
00:32:18,570 --> 00:32:21,369
So Oncology is mad at me.
Why do you suppose that is?

568
00:32:22,073 --> 00:32:23,564
I've had my hands full, Robert.

569
00:32:23,742 --> 00:32:27,042
Well, I just used all my pull
and influence to persuade them...

570
00:32:27,212 --> 00:32:30,114
to keep the chemo suite open
