00:32:33,518 --> 00:32:35,214
- I'm still...
- Stop complaining.

573
00:32:35,387 --> 00:32:37,913
Nobody told you to
go and get cancer.

574
00:32:51,303 --> 00:32:53,204
I have to go.

575
00:32:53,705 --> 00:32:55,970
I'll be back as soon as I can.

576
00:32:56,174 --> 00:32:58,040
You never answered my question.

577
00:33:00,712 --> 00:33:03,238
