583
00:34:54,793 --> 00:34:58,423
crack one open when something
really amazing happens.

584
00:34:59,831 --> 00:35:03,563
In five years here, this is
like the third one I've drunk.

585
00:35:06,071 --> 00:35:08,336
One beer every 20
months I can overlook.

586
00:35:09,908 --> 00:35:13,743
So forgive me for noticing...

587
00:35:14,379 --> 00:35:16,507
but what happened in there?

588
00:35:16,681 --> 00:35:18,377
Something changed.

589
00:35:20,352 --> 00:35:21,911
The situation evolved.

590
00:35:26,057 --> 00:35:27,525
It was a kid, right?

591
00:35:29,094 --> 00:35:30,960
We all have one.

592
00:35:32,864 --> 00:35:35,197
Some case you blew.

593
00:35:35,367 --> 00:35:37,598
