595
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:43,133
Yeah.

596
00:35:43,942 --> 00:35:45,638
How old?

597
00:35:49,481 --> 00:35:50,972
He was 5 years old.

598
00:35:52,417 --> 00:35:53,646
Those are the worst.

599
00:35:55,086 --> 00:35:56,611
He was my son.

600
00:35:56,788 --> 00:35:58,848
He died here.

601
00:36:01,159 --> 00:36:03,151
In Trauma 1.

602
00:36:05,997 --> 00:36:08,592
Your son died in this ER?

603
00:36:11,603 --> 00:36:12,935
And you're working here?

604
00:36:17,909 --> 00:36:20,811
