him in earlier.

630
00:39:06,277 --> 00:39:09,907
He had acute leukemia,
that's why he died.

631
00:39:10,448 --> 00:39:13,475
It might have given
me another day.

632
00:39:14,419 --> 00:39:15,478
A little more time.

633
00:39:21,926 --> 00:39:23,554
They said we can go now.

634
00:39:32,971 --> 00:39:36,635
I appreciate your
effort, Dr. Greene.

635
00:39:38,643 --> 00:39:41,704
Take care, both of you.

636
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:44,181
Good luck.

637
00:40:06,137 --> 00:40:07,867
Baby.

638
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,741
Where are you?

639
00:40:32,196 --> 00:40:34,688
