640
00:40:35,934 --> 00:40:37,926
At the hospital...

641
00:40:38,236 --> 00:40:40,068
at the funeral.

642
00:40:41,172 --> 00:40:42,902
I've been...

643
00:40:43,875 --> 00:40:46,538
I've been really
angry about that.

644
00:40:47,011 --> 00:40:50,743
You never cried about
anything since that day.

645
00:40:54,018 --> 00:40:56,920
Maybe we've been
fooling ourselves. Maybe...

646
00:40:57,088 --> 00:40:59,284
we've been done
