00:41:00,258 --> 00:41:02,454
never figured it out.

648
00:41:03,695 --> 00:41:05,095
I never blamed you.

649
00:41:06,798 --> 00:41:08,391
Never.

650
00:41:25,717 --> 00:41:28,551
I used to think
every day that...

651
00:41:29,954 --> 00:41:31,479
if God told me I could die...

652
00:41:31,689 --> 00:41:34,955
and go to heaven and
be with Daryl, I would do it.

653
00:41:37,428 --> 00:41:41,229
I wondered if that made
me an awful person...

654
00:41:41,399 --> 00:41:44,597
